      "path": "audio/narrations/levy-c-curve/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.0,
      "size": 31968,
      "text": "眼前这条曲线，是由无数个字母 C 层层叠叠拼成的。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "levy-c-curve",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/levy-c-curve/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.23,
      "size": 35712,
      "text": "它叫列维C形曲线，由数学家保罗·列维在上世纪提出。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "levy-c-curve",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/levy-c-curve/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.83,
      "size": 29232,
      "text": "别看它形状复杂，生成规则却简单得出人意料。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "levy-c-curve",
      "section_id": "rule",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "rule-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/levy-c-curve/xiaoxiao/rule-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33984,
      "text": "从一条水平线段开始，把它当作一个等腰直角三角形的斜边。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "levy-c-curve",
      "section_id": "rule",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "rule-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/levy-c-curve/xiaoxiao/rule-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.3,
      "size": 36864,
      "text": "用两条直角边替换这条斜边，一条线段就变成了折起的两段。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "levy-c-curve",
      "section_id": "rule",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "rule-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/levy-c-curve/xiaoxiao/rule-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.49,
      "size": 23760,
      "text": "这一步替换，正是整条曲线的基本笔画。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "levy-c-curve",
      "section_id": "recurse",
      "line_id": "rec-1",
      "filename": "recurse-rec-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/levy-c-curve/xiaoxiao/recurse-rec-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29376,
      "text": "接着，对新生成的每一条线段，重复同样的替换。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "levy-c-curve",
      "section_id": "recurse",
      "line_id": "rec-2",
      "filename": "recurse-rec-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/levy-c-curve/xiaoxiao/recurse-rec-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.99,
      "size": 31824,
      "text": "每提升一阶，线段数量就翻倍，图形迅速变得繁复。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "levy-c-curve",
      "section_id": "recurse",
      "line_id": "rec-3",
      "filename": "recurse-rec-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/levy-c-curve/xiaoxiao/recurse-rec-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.4,
      "size": 38448,
      "text": "放大任何一个角落，都能看到和整体一模一样的 C 形，这就是自相似。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "levy-c-curve",
      "section_id": "dimension",
      "line_id": "dim-1",
      "filename": "dimension-dim-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/levy-c-curve/xiaoxiao/dimension-dim-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.04,
      "size": 32688,
      "text": "这条曲线的分形维数接近 2，几乎要填满一整片平面。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "levy-c-curve",
      "section_id": "dimension",
      "line_id": "dim-2",
      "filename": "dimension-dim-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/levy-c-curve/xiaoxiao/dimension-dim-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.64,
      "size": 26208,
      "text": "它是一条一维的线，却拥有近乎二维的复杂度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "levy-c-curve",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/levy-c-curve/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.22,
      "size": 35568,
      "text": "调整递归阶数，看它从简单折线一步步长成饱满的 C 形团。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "levy-c-curve",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/levy-c-curve/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32256,
      "text": "阶数越高，边缘的褶皱越细密，细节仿佛无穷无尽。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "levy-c-curve",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/levy-c-curve/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.34,
      "size": 37440,
      "text": "列维C曲线把每条线段替换成等腰直角三角形的两条直角边。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "levy-c-curve",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/levy-c-curve/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32256,
      "text": "一遍遍递归后，简单规则生成了无穷自相似的分形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "levy-c-curve",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/levy-c-curve/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "简单孕育复杂，正是分形的迷人之处，我们下次再见！"
    }
